44
00:01:58,900 --> 00:02:00,950
I wish you all the best of luck.

45
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:07,510
Brother Wen Chang, it's your turn.

46
00:02:09,950 --> 00:02:10,550
Where is he?

47
00:02:11,890 --> 00:02:12,560
Where is he?

48
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:13,430
Brother Wen Chang!

49
